data.description: *** New Attractive Price***   Stunning   3 levels, 2 car garage townhome in Dorchester View built by Lennar in 2016.   Bright Airy Open floor plan,  3bed/2 full baths/ 2 half bath,  Gorgeous Gourmet  Kitchen w/ Customized Range hood,  backsplash, Double Wall Oven,  Gas cooktop, SS Appliances, a Large Island,   designated dining area, walk in panty, deck off the kitchen is perfect for outdoor, and laundry is located in upper bedroom level.  Upgraded light fixtures.   Great location, Minutes from Ft Meade, NSA, Arundel Mills attractions, major highways  295,100, 95, 32, 29 .  Easy commute to  Baltimore and Washington DC.    Absolutely beautiful home and MUST SEE HOME!!!
